Package ca.ualberta.cs.corgFuViews

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddLocationToQuestionFragment
    This is a custom Dialog Fragment that handles upon login whether or not a user would like to attach their location to any questions they post.
    AddPictureActivity  
    AddPictureDialogFragment
    Activity (Dialog Fragment) that is responsible for prompting the user the choice whether of attaching an image to their answer/question and if yes, redirect them to their android picture gallery to select and image.
    AddSmallerPictureDialog
    Dialog Fragment responsible for asking a user if he/she wants to add smaller picture.
    BrowseItems
    The activity that Allows users to browse through the currently available questions that are present in the AllQuestions model.
    CreateLocationActivity
    This activity handles when the user would like to select their own username.
    LoginActivity
    The LoginActivity Activity handles setting the global username for the session , it also saves the user preference of whether or not they would like to attach their location to questions that they post.
    MainActivity
    This is the MainActivity Activity.
    MyProfile
    This is the activity that contains several choices of content that the user would like to see.
    OfflineDataView
    The activity that contains the data that has been made offline and been made to view offline such as the users authored questions, viewed, favorited and chosen to read later
    SearchResults
    The activity that displays the search results of a search.
    ViewAnswerAndReplies
    Activity that is responsible for showing a Question.
    ViewQuestionAndAnswers
    Activity that is responsible for showing a Question.
    ViewQuestionAndReplies
    Activity that is responsible for showing a Question.
